Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Yukimori
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They've made the new Division 5\Npersonnel assignments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Effective today, F Squad will be led by\NLieutenant Ishimaru, formerly of A Squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and former squad leader Sawazaki and\NDivision 1 Asami will take orders from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I get to work with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for it. Demanded it, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was A Squad's Kikuhara\Nwho pushed for the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, they didn't have any plans\Nto add anyone to F Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But then out of nowhere, he started claiming\Nyou can't control your devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It just didn't sit right with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't trust him. Him or the new leader\Nhe was so eager replace you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A new leader, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's in charge, I'll have to\Nintroduce him to Anzai and Jill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But you won't introduce me to anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the state of the scene\Nand witness testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a strong possibility that the missing\NRyunosuke Katagiri was shot and injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, there is no indication that you,\Na former investigator of Division 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,have gone to any hospitals to look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you already know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer Anzai took custody of a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was acting in concert with\Nan unidentified foreign man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to introduce me to\Neveryone who is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an order from your superior officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The overlapping moments
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We might believe them to be eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The labyrinthine sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Begs for light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The impulse eats away at me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:02:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Libido erases my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Into darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have fallen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a hideous form
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If my human tears have dried
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NOur crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wets our bond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NWe share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we two live on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Licking each other's wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Defining each other's life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirsting for love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Command
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to see his face like this every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we're living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about having another base of operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakaki said he'll let you use his warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Be careful, it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, sorry to interrupt, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki wants you downstairs.\NOur new boss is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,New boss? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But he wants everybody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally he'd just want the squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my fault.\NThey found out I ignored the standby order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you blaming yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Lieutenant Ishimaru, formerly of A Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today, he is F Squad's new leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm now a regular member,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and Asami from Divison 1 will be\Non our team temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I get tired of formalities,\Nso don't worry about being extra polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Anzai, Miss Hostage,\NYanagi, Mr. Foreigner, and Miss Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see Katagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have more bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For the next two months,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai and Jill are forbidden from\Ngoing outside without a human chaperon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to only apply to work, but now you're\Nprohibited from going out for personal reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we have to put up with that kind of crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And we don't need a new boss. I like Sawazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do your job by playing best buds, Miss Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I don't understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now we have to focus on solving this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd like to hear about what happened at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me. What do I do about...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he's a spy, like Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a dilemma, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you tell him? Can you trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I wouldn't trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Asami, then I want you\Nto do a background check on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need to prove you can trust me before you\Ncan work on this case, then you should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And investigate Inspector Kikuhara while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikuhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was Kikuhara's idea to demote Sawazaki\Nand appoint me as squad leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go on and do your background checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is sit down and shut up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So then Nine gave me this.\NHe said it was an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}If you have any trouble,\N{\an5}post a message here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But, um, Nine and Seven left the CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping we could use this\Nwithout arresting them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}If you have any trouble,\N{\an5}post a message here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But to use this in a way that doesn't screw them over...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to contact them\Nand get them to come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... not a devil, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're referring to my eyes, this is because\NI stay up late reading manga and light novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike yours, my dark circles\Nare a sign of poor health.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That being the case, Miss Hostage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you get a gold star for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So the whole Ikebukuro Incident\Nwas staged by the CCC
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to sway public opinion toward eradicating all devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, about Zero Five aka Ushio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to report him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do, it will go straight to\Ngeneral commander Kikuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Wasn't it Kikuhara\Nwho deployed Ushio to the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kikuhara does happen to be with the CCC,\Nhe'd let Ushio get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,True, if it's going to add to the number of\Nguerilla operatives we can't monitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then it'd be better to leave him in Division 5\Nwhere others can keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikuhara may be a person of interest, but I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That is exactly why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to contact Zero Seven and Zero Nine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and negotiate with them\Nto give us information on the CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to work with wanted criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll think about whether or not to arrest them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I'm counting on your help, Miss Hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to add her to the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how much danger\Nshe's already been through?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's the only one who has a rapport with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, she'll be fine as long as\Nshe has you, won't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're much more reliable than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're worried then you can\Njoin the negotiations team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave her our web address?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}One new post\N{\an4}Subject: I need some advice\NBut we did get her in a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she traces us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can erase the site itself, and I did set things up\Nto make sure no one could identify us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Nine, did you manage to get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Seven healing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for contacting you like this. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that we can protect you\Nand Seven, and capture the CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When are the negotiations going down?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In three days. I'm so glad\NSeven and Nine answered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you wanted to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought I'd like a little free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get some... necessities, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your phone so I can input my number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your curfew is 6:00 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're doing this, you could\Ngive me your number, too, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When you saved Tsukasa the other day\Nand you dodged me, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it was because you thought I'd take her from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I was serious when I said\NI'd take her off your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back or else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling a little more\Ncomfortable with Lee, Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno. Maybe I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Two evening doses\Nand two morning doses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Feng, you can't draw that much all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I've got plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I have to stop asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know a person can only give\Nso much blood. You're a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Single-eye transformation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The transformation only affects one part\Nof your body, and you keep your sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the special privilege of a half-breed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I hear I'm the only one who's ever managed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe it's your own special power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna teach this other half-devil\NI know some blood tolerance, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You mean you've made a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that where you're staying now?\NWith that friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, it's kind of a big home\Nwhere lots of people stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how big is the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that it changes color\Ndepending on the time of day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The "sky" is an endless space\Nthat stretches out above the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back as soon as I've observed the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come back, they'll never let you leave again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more than just the sky\Nthat you need to learn about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide for yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back or else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a big happy family,\Nin the place you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not part of that family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They're only keeping me there\Nbecause I can teach him blood tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When that's over, they'll be done with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the half-devil you're teaching like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a scaredy-cat who acts tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,His girlfriend is surprisingly impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're a couple of big crybabies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The polar opposite of you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Try thinking of that place as home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Cafe\N{\an7}Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't trust you police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't trust you 100 percent yet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now allow me to present our terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One: We will prepare an apartment for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Two: We will provide living expenses\Nand necessary funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And three: we won't arrest you. For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"For now"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a cowardly phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also an honest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And? What do you get out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Any information you have on the CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A list or roster of members, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I could get a look at their financials\Nif I hack into the hideout's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this, Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get them a roster,\Nboth our names will be on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In all honesty, we could arrest you both right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We want a roster so we can crush the entire CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still not worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then give us some terms. Make it worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a devil who died\N15 years ago, Kenichi Morisawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Chizu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a well-behaved child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For some time, she hated\Nto even see the word "devil."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know when it happened,\Nbut at one point I realized she'd gotten over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotten over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Suddenly, she was\Nbringing up the subject herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But she sounded biased against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I did tell her to stop once...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}Morisawa, Kenichi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Search results: 1\N{\an5}Display                        Cancel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Classified I:069
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cases marked "I" or "Inside,"\Nrequire special permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they were done on the inside.\NThey're police scandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Morisawa, Kenichi\N{\an5}Public Security\N{\an5}Division 5 Section 2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenichi Morisawa, age 32 at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Public Security Division 5, Section 2, AR Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Tenjo, Sayuri\N{\an5}Hachioji City Hall\N{\an5}Civic Affairs Division 2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Seven's mother, Sayuri Tenjo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Age 33 at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Worked at Hachioji City Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A widow who lived alone with her daughter Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They dated for about a year, and Morisawa\Neventually started spending nights at her home,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,where he spent more time\Nplaying with her daughter Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one night, Morisawa gave Nanako a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When she saw it, Sayuri pulled out a gun\Nand shot him. That's how it all began.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If she shot him, does that mean\NMorisawa had transformed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayuri's diary had a passage about him\Nconsulting her about his bloodlust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Any records about Morisawa's work attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He was extremely hardworking and good at his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,His personality was kind and sociable.\NHe didn't talk about himself much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayuri's bullet missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Morisawa immediately\Ntook the gun from her and fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As she lay dying, he drank her blood and raped her,\Nright there in front of her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako panicked and stole the gun again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:15:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She "fired it by mistake" and\Nshot Morisawa through the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Seven had a crush on Morisawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't you mean Morisawa had a thing for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's just a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're little, you tend to fall in love\Nwith the grownups who are closest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it was a crush or familial love,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but you may be right that she admired him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be very sad to be the one\Nto kill the person you care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go inside. We'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing someone I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared to even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether she meant to kill him or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it wounded her deeply, and she closed off her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, after a certain incident,\Nshe started coming out against devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who took her in, Kousuke Chizu,\Nwas a professor at East Bay University.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He would hold study sessions at his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she have an opportunity to interact\Nwith any of the students?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There was someone who\Ngave her justification for killing devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Lecturer: Kaname Shirase\N{\an7}(Member, House of Representatives - New Civil Party)\N{\an5}Date & Time:  May 22 (Sun), 2005  2:00 p.m.\N{\an5}Students in attendance:\N{\an5}Shouji Muto\N{\an5}Youhei Tanuma\N{\an5}Makoto Aizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Kirio Kikuhara\N{\an5}Takashi Katayama
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who convinced her it was right\Nto kill them, that it's right to hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Kirio Kikuhara
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who gave her peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back now. You'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we should help them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, if we're on the run,\Nthen it would put us at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to stop Kikuhara from\Nkilling any more people, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like him, Zero Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well, I always thought you might like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just from watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good at math. Want me to tutor you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Practice Exam Student Score Report
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardship is what gives us\Nthe greatest opportunity to grow stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspect apprehended at 21:01.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me. Look me in the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, devils will be driven out of our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Driven out? Where will they...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they'll just be left to find their own place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we don't segregate them or exterminate them,\Nthere will be more like Morisawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with anyone. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you as a woman,\Nand I'll never look at you sexually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can understand that, then join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I wanted to think I understood,\Nbut I didn't really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He warned me.\NHe told me not to fall in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because falling in love with Kikuhara...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,made me forget my fear of Morisawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I adored Kikuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything on Morisawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you one thing first?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Had Morisawa ever drunk blood before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she can find it in her heart\Nto forgive Morisawa, or any devil, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, instead of thinking she\Nhad killed the individual Morisawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it was easier for her to think\Nshe'd killed one of a different species.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you learn anything new?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like I remembered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So we failed to live up to your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was everything I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine and I will help you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop Kikuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Kikuhara is working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He is Zero Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Practically the leader of the CCC.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, with only your testimony,\Nhe just needs to play innocent, and we're through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Exterminate the devil pests!\NUnfortunately, with only your testimony,\Nhe just needs to play innocent, and we're through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, with only your testimony,\Nhe just needs to play innocent, and we're through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Exterminate the devil pests!\NUnfortunately, with only your testimony,\Nhe just needs to play innocent, and we're through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}Vampires really do exist!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Don't let the Ikebukuro\N{\an5}tragedy happen again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Segregate now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Most humans first found out about devils\Nafter the Ikebukuro Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But some of them already knew and didn't like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the Devil Vigilante Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil Vigilante Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There are some radicals in with the protestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something not right about-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Jill! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! We're the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume the CCC has nothing to do with this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like they let us in on all their plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Sawazaki and Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check things out and meet up with them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed to go out without a chape-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there. That counts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a devil. Cause any problems\Nunder these circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can bet your punishment\Nwill be worse than a little house arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens, whatever you do,\Ndo not get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!\NNow is the time to stand together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!\NWe will all defeat the devils together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look! They're waving blood around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they trying to expose the devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Stop hiding the devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop hiding the devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil's running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Call Division 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna help that devil get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just leave her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I get to be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I give chase,\Nthe deeper the devils run into the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I overtake them, arrest them, and take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The process is ingrained into my muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I stop myself from going after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At least carry some sedatives with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest for a while and you'll be able to walk again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew if I kept hunting devils,\NI'd run into you eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is supposed to be the Vigilantes' live broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ochiai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:22:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like softly melting away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could have loved each other more like that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I have told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance encounter that cannot amount to love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this filthy form is who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.42,0:22:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these fingers trembling as they touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of fighting together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hold you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.71,0:22:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect you without hurting you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You and only you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.67,0:22:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of desiring forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Against the urges surging up inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, again, I..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.92,0:23:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we're softly melting away...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,DEVILS' LINE,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Line 10,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ego Defense."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Ego Defense